Description: Enabling authenticating of users from different identity providers in 'Shiny'
    using 'oAuth2' protocol. Currently supporting 'Auth0' and 'Keycloak'.
    Federation to other identity providers like 'Azure', 'Google', 'Github', 'Facebook' and others is possible through 'Auth0' and 'Keycloak'.
    Multi factor authentication is also an option.
